## 2. Open Source Edition (AGPL-3.0)

### 2.1 License

The Open Source Edition is licensed under the GNU Affero General Public License
version 3 (AGPL-3.0). AGPL-3.0 is the Affero version of the GNU General Public
License, published by the Free Software Foundation. A copy of the AGPL-3.0
